---
/**
 * EmptyState component for the gallery page.
 * Displays a friendly message when no panels are available yet.
 */
---

<div class="empty-state">
  <h2>Panel Gallery Coming Soon</h2>
  <p>
    The Council panel library is under active development. Check back soon for
    pre-built expert panels covering various disciplines.
  </p>
</div>

<style>
  .empty-state {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    color: var(--sl-color-text-accent);
  }

  .empty-state h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .empty-state p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 40rem;
    margin-inline: auto;
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
  }
</style>
